Reasoning: The paper proposes a method for designing neural network models for a robotic task involving stacking colored blocks, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The method involves combining parts of other architectures, which suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the proposed method using a dataset and introduces a new benchmark, which aligns with the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
